createestrogen.ponder.basic.text_1: The Centrifuge doesn't have any inventory, you will need to place fluid containers around it to make it work!
createestrogen.ponder.basic.text_2: You can input fluids from the bottom
createestrogen.ponder.basic.text_3: And output fluids from the top
createestrogen.ponder.intro.text_1: The Centrifuge needs the maximum speed (256 RPM) to work!
